Intro(String title = "Oobium Routing")

title {title}

p This guide covers the features of Oobium routing. By referring to this guide, you will be able to:
ul.intro
	li Construct your own routes, using RESTful and adhoc styles
	li Automatically create paths and URLs
	li Add parameters that can be received in an action
	li Publish your routes as public and private API
	li Protect your routes and assets with Basic Authentication
